<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Other processes primarily maintain the alliance rather than fire. Fire is extremely rare in stands of very low cover. More regular disturbances include mass movement of colluvium and processes that create patterned ground.</div>
